content:
Customizing Reports in Salesforce Classic

The report builder is a visual editor for reports. It lets you work with report fields and filters, and shows a preview of your report with some data.

Available in: Group, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

Fields Pane:

* Find fields using Quick Find search box and field type filters.
* Drag fields into the Preview pane to add them to the report.
* Create, view, edit, and delete custom summary formulas and bucket fields.

Filters Pane:

* Set view, time frame, and custom filters to limit data shown in the report.

Preview Pane:

* Add, reorder, and remove columns, summary fields, formulas, groupings, and blocks.
* Change report format and display options, or add a chart.
* The preview shows only a limited number of records. Run the report to see all results.

Report Fields in Salesforce Classic
title: Customizing Reports in Salesforce
